request.description:
Complete admin registration using an invitation token sent via POST /admins/invite. Sets the account password and activates the account.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "Account activated successfully.",
  "user": {
    "id": "admin-009",
    "name": "New Moderator",
    "email": "newmod@snaptik.com",
    "role": "moderator"
  }
}
```

Returns aggregate platform statistics: total users, DAU, videos uploaded, flagged content count, open tickets, and revenue metrics.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "users": {
    "total": 1240385,
    "activeToday": 87432,
    "newThisWeek": 12043,
    "banned": 3201
  },
  "content": {
    "totalVideos": 9823411,
    "uploadedToday": 45120,
    "flaggedPending": 342
  },
  "tickets": {
    "open": 87,
    "urgent": 12
  },
  "revenue": {
    "mrr": 128450.00,
    "todayRevenue": 4230.50
  }
}
```

Returns active system alerts requiring admin attention (e.g. high error rates, flagged content spikes, infrastructure warnings).

