request.description:
Returns a paginated list of AI-flagged content awaiting human review. Includes confidence scores, flag categories (nsfw, violence, spam, hate, csam), and uploader info.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "vid-001",
      "uploaderId": "usr-042",
      "uploaderUsername": "badactor99",
      "thumbnailUrl": "https://cdn.snaptik.app/thumb/vid-001.jpg",
      "flagCategory": "nsfw",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "status": "pending",
      "flaggedAt": "2026-03-15T08:12:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 342, "pages": 18 }
}
```

Filter flagged content by `status` (pending|approved|rejected|deleted) and/or `minConfidence` (0.0–1.0). Useful for prioritizing high-confidence violations.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "vid-007",
      "flagCategory": "violence",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "status": "pending",
      "flaggedAt": "2026-03-15T09:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 89, "pages": 5 }
}
```

