request.description:
Returns a paginated list of all user-submitted reports. Supports query params: `status` (pending|resolved|dismissed), `type` (video|user|comment), `assignedTo`.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "reports": [
    {
      "id": "rep-001",
      "type": "video",
      "targetId": "vid-042",
      "reportedBy": "usr-100",
      "reason": "harassment",
      "description": "This video targets me personally with threats.",
      "status": "pending",
      "assignedTo": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-14T15:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 1043, "pages": 53 }
}
```

Filter reports by status. Use `status=pending` to show only unresolved reports requiring action.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "reports": [
    {
      "id": "rep-001",
      "status": "pending",
      "reason": "harassment",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-14T15:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 231, "pages": 12 }
}
```

body.raw:
{
  "action": "warn",
  "notes": "Reviewed video — language is aggressive but does not meet threshold for removal. User warned per policy 3.1."
}

request.description:
Returns a paginated list of all support tickets. Supports filtering by `status` (open|in_progress|waiting|resolved|closed) and `priority` (low|normal|high|urgent).

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "tickets": [
    {
      "id": "tkt-001",
      "subject": "My account was wrongfully banned",
      "userId": "usr-042",
      "userEmail": "user@example.com",
      "status": "open",
      "priority": "high",
      "category": "account",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-13T11:00:00Z",
      "lastReplyAt": null
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 87, "pages": 5 }
}
```

Filter for open urgent tickets requiring immediate attention.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "tickets": [
    {
      "id": "tkt-009",
      "subject": "CSAM reported via ticket",
      "status": "open",
      "priority": "urgent",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-15T07:20:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 12, "pages": 1 }
}
```

