request.description:
Returns user growth time-series data for the specified period. Includes daily new signups, churn, and net growth. Query param `days` supports: 7, 14, 30, 90, 365.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "days": 30,
  "series": [
    { "date": "2026-02-14", "newUsers": 3421, "churned": 234, "net": 3187 },
    { "date": "2026-02-15", "newUsers": 3890, "churned": 201, "net": 3689 }
  ],
  "totals": {
    "newUsers": 98450,
    "churned": 6830,
    "net": 91620
  }
}
```

Returns content engagement metrics: daily uploads, views, likes, shares, comments, average watch time, and top-performing content categories.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "uploads": { "today": 45120, "thisWeek": 312340 },
  "engagement": {
    "avgWatchTime": 22.8,
    "likeRate": 0.078,
    "shareRate": 0.021
  },
  "topCategories": [
    { "name": "Dance", "viewShare": 0.31 },
    { "name": "Comedy", "viewShare": 0.24 },
    { "name": "DIY", "viewShare": 0.11 }
  ]
}
```

Returns a paginated, chronological list of all admin actions. Each entry records: who performed the action, what action, on which target, from which IP, and at what time.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "aud-001",
      "adminId": "admin-001",
      "adminEmail": "admin@snaptik.com",
      "action": "user.ban",
      "targetType": "user",
      "targetId": "usr-042",
      "metadata": { "reason": "Spam" },
      "ip": "192.168.1.10",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-15T10:45:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 50, "total": 24890, "pages": 498 }
}
```

Filter audit log by `action` (e.g. user.ban, user.warn, content.delete, settings.update), `from` and `to` date (ISO 8601), and optionally `adminId`.

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "aud-201",
      "action": "user.ban",
      "targetId": "usr-099",
      "metadata": { "reason": "CSAM" },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-10T14:20:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 50, "total": 18, "pages": 1 }
}
```

